For In Vitro Diagnostic Use Only. The Alinity m HCV assay is an in vitro reverse transcription-polymerase chain reaction (RT-PCR) assay for use with the automated Alinity m System to detect and quantitate HCV RNA in human serum samples. This assay is intended for use in the clinical management of HCV infected patients undergoing antiviral therapy in conjunction with clinical presentation and other laboratory markers, monitoring disease prognosis by measuring the baseline plasma HCV DNA level to assess viral response to antiretroviral treatment by measuring changes in plasma HCV DNA levels and may also be used as a diagnostic test to aid in the diagnosis of HCV. This assay is intended for use in clinical management of infected individuals in conjunction with clinical presentation and other laboratory makers and must be interpreted within the context of all relevant clinical and laboratory findings.
